N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4230.8 - Claim irrevocable when lodged

State Regulations

When a claim has been lodged with the secretary or clerk
of the course, it is irrevocable, and is at the risk of the
claimant. Notes
